lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"處處都是紅線，遲啲真係所有節目都揾林奠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林奠大波驊版五夜講場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:21:12.000Z","msg":"可能出年CCTVB 開套劇畀鄭月娥"},{"pid":"4d616ec5738ba8ecbfb9791d46c587e0e83efa65","tid":2515333,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"23f6939b0e9f6111c8755bad7fea6c7dd0aa3148","tid":2515333,"uid":52779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:11:55.000Z","msg":"Backup RTHK 所有節目<br />\n總之所有yt冇嘅都去 <a href=\"http://podcast.rthk.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpodcast.rthk.hk&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=2c61e5ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">podcast.rthk.hk</a> 睇<br />\n<br />\n請參考以下Google Doc，入面有不同影片進度同教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1I3yYU2CTjlDt39xOZaSf7Qjj87eArrqEDp4897SaaSw/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1I3yYU2CTjlDt39xOZaSf7Qjj87eArrqEDp4897SaaSw%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=48d5f450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1I3yYU2CTjlDt39xOZaSf7Qjj87eArrqEDp4897SaaSw/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n另有整理資源用大Google Sheet，backup完可以幫手整理：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=66302e8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗YouTube之外，可以到RTHK Podcast官網backup<br />\n有啲片可能YouTube del咗，但係官網未！<br />\n<a href=\"https://podcast.rthk.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcast.rthk.hk%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=b13a96a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://podcast.rthk.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n提提大家Podcast最好講清楚係Podcast Video定真。淨係得聲嘅Podcast<br />\n<br />\nTUTORIAL 教學 (無圖)<br />\n===========================<br />\n1. YouTube下載可以用youtube-dl + lbry publish<br />\n<a href=\"https://odysee.com/@code:a/kit:d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fodysee.com%2F%40code%3Aa%2Fkit%3Ad&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=8cda8931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://odysee.com/@code:a/kit:d</a><br />\n//This could be very useful if you lost access to a video or if you want to backup something and you don't have the youtube sync turned on. It also works as a limited version of of youtube-dl if you want to download .mp4 or .mp3   To sum up youtube-dl + lbry publish //<br />\n<br />\n2. Curl command批量下載港台Podcast 教學<br />\nI. 用chrome是旦搵一個channel(右click禁&rdquo;檢查&rdquo;)<br />\nII. 入到一版可以睇到晒所有片<br />\nIII. 禁最先果條片(eg. 20200101), 對住下載果個制禁&rdquo;檢查&rdquo;<br />\nIV. 你會見到隔離dev tool出左條link, 先記低呢條link<br />\nV. 開terminal，用mac機做demo。先係terminal到打 &ldquo;pwd&rdquo;(present working directory)，會出番你依家係邊個folder，d片就係down係果度<br />\n<br />\nVI. 佢20170101果條片既pattern係由S01000001開始，<br />\npath: <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000001.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01000001.mp4&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=c7ffa94c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000001.mp4</a> <br />\n<br />\n仲係...2017S01000既pattern既最後一條片應該係10月26<br />\npath : <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000205.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01000205.mp4&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=a3eb0829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000205.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n所以我地download 左呢個pattern既片先。作用： download由20170101 － 20171026既片<br />\ncurl -O <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000[001-205].mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01000%5B001-205%5D.mp4&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=9afc9b31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01000[001-205].mp4</a> <br />\n<br />\nVII. 如果你直接禁2017年最後一條片就發覺佢既pattern唔同左。跟住我就搵埋下一個pattern既第一條片係咩（好似係2017年既10月27定28號）<br />\n<br />\n新pattern係由&rdquo;<a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01100001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01100001&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=0a02b2ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01100001</a> 去到 <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01100055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S01100055&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=a39770b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S01100055</a> 。<br />\n去番terminal果到輸入以下既command: <br />\ncurl -O <a href=\"https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S011000[01-55].mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.rthk.hk%2Fmp4%2Ftv%2F2017%2FPEPXCT2017S011000%5B01-55%5D.mp4&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=b2465c0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://archive.rthk.hk/mp4/tv/2017/PEPXCT2017S011000[01-55].mp4</a>  <br />\n<br />\nVIII. 完成。你應該會見到佢down緊，不過係會有d慢。我發覺有d係會down左但係播唔到，有時間可以double check, 感謝！！"}}